WEBVTT

00:06:58.600 --> 00:07:01.056
or 'A Black Woman Got A Job?'"

00:07:01.080 --> 00:07:04.216
Because without confronting
men's sense of entitlement,

00:07:04.240 --> 00:07:08.536
I don't think we'll ever understand
why so many men resist gender equality.

00:07:08.560 --> 00:07:14.976
(Applause)

00:07:15.000 --> 00:07:18.336
Look, we think this
is a level playing field,

00:07:18.360 --> 00:07:20.536
so any policy that tilts it
even a little bit,

00:07:20.560 --> 00:07:22.696
we think, "Oh my God,
water's rushing uphill.

00:07:22.720 --> 00:07:24.625
It's reverse discrimination against us."

00:07:24.649 --> 00:07:25.856
(Laughter)

00:07:25.880 --> 00:07:27.280
So let me be very clear:

00:07:27.880 --> 00:07:30.896
white men in Europe and the United States